snippet.title: Sniper Elite 4 | First Gameplay Trailer & Target Führer Teaser
snippet.description:
Buy at Amazon (UK) - PS4/Xbox One: https://amzn.to/2ICjGa4 
Buy at Amazon (USA) – PS4: https://amzn.to/39HDMvr

Watch the explosive debut gameplay trailer for Sniper Elite 4 featuring new kill cams, new takedowns, new stealth abilities and the most satisfying sniping in the series to date. 

Don't forget to stay to the end for a surprise Target Führer mission reveal!

Follow us on:
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/rebellion_official/
